{{Quick Guide}}

==Details==
{{Quest details page|The Eyes of Glouphrie}}

==Walkthrough==
===Digression===
{{Checklist|
*Talk to [[Brimstail]] in the cave found in the south-west corner of the Gnome Stronghold. {{Chat option|1What's that cute creature wandering around?|1Yes, that sounds fascinating...|1Oh, yes I love a bit of History.|1Of course!}}
}}

===Elven Mystery===
{{Checklist|
*Inspect the singing bowl in the western portion of the cave.
*To the north, attempt to unlock Oaknock's Machine.
*Talk to Brimstail. {{Chat option|1I've had a look in the other room now.|1Of course, I'd love to!}}
}}

===Memories===
{{Checklist|
*Talk to [[Hazelmere]], located upstairs in his house (on the small island east of Yanille, fairy ring code {{fairycode|cls}} goes directly to his house, [[Nightmare Zone]] [[minigame teleport]] or Watchtower Teleport). There will be several cutscenes, last being King Healthorg and the white Spirit Tree Argento .
*Return to Brimstail. {{Chat option|1I've visited Hazelmere, he told me all sorts of interesting things.}}
}}

===Incapacitated===
{{Needed|[[Hammer]], [[Pestle and Mortar]], [[Saw]], [[Mud rune]], [[Bucket of sap]], [[Maple logs]], [[Oak logs]]}}
{{Checklist|
*Use your Mud Rune on the Pestle and Mortar to make Ground Mud Runes.
*Add the Ground Mud Runes to the Bucket of Sap.
*Repair Oaknock's machine (click on the machine twice).
*Talk to Brimstail. {{Chat option|1I think I've fixed the machine now!}}
}}

===Anti-Illusion===
{{Checklist|
*Talk to Brimstail twice more to receive more discs. {{Chat option|1I }}
*'''Optional''': Drop the discs and talk to Brimstail to receive even more discs. {{Chat option|1I can't work out what to do with these discs!}}
}}

===Front Panel===
{{Checklist|
*Unlock machine.
}}

===Control Panel===
{{Checklist|
*Unlock the front panel by inserting a disc with a value equal to the green number. (When done, click the green box next to the number.)
*Talk to Brimstail for more discs. {{Chat option|1I }}
*Complete the three puzzles inside the unlocked machine
**You need to fill up every slot, the first puzzle's single slot, the second's two slots, and the last puzzle's three slots.
**You will need to exchange some of the tokens to obtain certain values. (see full guide [[The Eyes of Glouphrie|here]]).
}}
{{Colour-shape value|align=right}}

{{Checklist|
*Talk to Brimstail. {{Chat option|1Phew! I've got that machine working now. What do I need to do now?}}}}

===Assassination===
{{Checklist|*Talk to Brimstail again. {{Chat option|1Phew! I've got that machine working now. What do I need to do now?}}
*Kill all Evil Creatures: (wait for the whole death animation to end before running or teleporting away!). Their colour is now black.
**The one by Brimstail, if you haven't killed it already.
**One outside of the main gate (south-east from Brimstail's cave). Note: It must be killed within stronghold walls. If it is outside, simply kill it, let it spawn, and kill it again for credit.
**One by the gnome agility course entrance (near the spirit tree).
**One by King Narnode, at the bottom of the Grand Tree. If it is stuck behind a trapdoor, kill it with mage or range, or hop worlds. Make sure you wait a few seconds after killing before using the ladder.
**One at the top of the Grand Tree, by the prison. '''Make sure you wait a few seconds after killing before using the ladder.'''
**One by the giant tortoises north-west of the Grand Tree (in the pen north of the swamp).
*Talk to King Narnode.
**Optional: Use the [[crystal saw seed]] on the [[singing bowl]] by Brimstail to get an enchanted [[crystal saw]], and complete a medium Western Provinces diary task.}}
'''Quest complete!'''

